{
  "id": "adv_event_2403_01_02",
  "title": "沖縄＆福岡",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――サニーピース全国ツアー初日in沖縄",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Sunny Peace National Tour‚ First Day in Okinawa",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "天気予報が雨だったから心配してたけど……\n綺麗な青空ね。よく晴れた気持ちのいい天気だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was worried because the weather forecast said it would rain…\nbut it’s a beautiful blue sky. What a nice‚ clear day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5666666905,
      "endTime": 11.5257367053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.726530512
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんが沖縄と相性が悪かったのは、昔の話……\n今は、沖縄と相性ばっちり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san didn’t get along with Okinawa… but it's the past…\nNow‚ you get along with Okinawa perfectly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.726530512,
      "endTime": 19.7970068531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.9978006599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、本当にその通りね\nそれじゃあ早速、特典映像の収録に向かいましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that's absolutely right.\nWell then‚ shall we head to the bonus footage recording right away?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9978006599,
      "endTime": 27.9902044531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.1909982599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は雫ちゃんのファンの夢を叶えるんだよね？\n会いに行くのは、雫ちゃんと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re making a dream come true for Shizuku-chan’s fan today‚ right?\nPeople who are meeting the fan today are… Shizuku-chan and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.1909982599,
      "endTime": 35.3834020532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5508599833
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "私と怜ちゃんの三人だよ\nそれで、今日はどんな夢を叶えるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…me and Rei-chan‚ the three!\nSo what dream are we making come true today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.5508599833,
      "endTime": 41.1300209597,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.31752665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "これから会うファンは、釣りが趣味……\n夢は……地元の沖縄で私と釣りをすること……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fan we're about to meet has fishing as a hobby…\nHis dream is… to fish with me in his hometown‚ Okinawa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.31752665,
      "endTime": 49.4775267834,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9382.472904900005
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 150173.40955650003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.7283205902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、今からみんなで堤防釣りをする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For that‚ we’re all going pier fishing now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7783205902,
      "endTime": 56.040202704600006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.2409965112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "本物の雫ちゃんが目の前にいる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The real Shizuku-chan is right in front of me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2409965112,
      "endTime": 60.2333303451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一緒に釣りが出来るなんて、夢みたいだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be able to fish with her… It's like a dream…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.2333303451,
      "endTime": 64.7334003044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "推しが目の前にいるのが信じられない気持ち、分かる\nでも夢じゃない……今日は一緒に釣り、頑張る……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand‚ the incredible feeling when your oshi is right in front of you.\nBut it’s not a dream… Let’s do our best fishing together today…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.9341941112,
      "endTime": 73.6160081142,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.8168019209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい！　よろしくお願いします！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Please take care of me!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.8168019209,
      "endTime": 76.54253548710001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.7433292937
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんのファンの人、凄く喜んでるよ\nサプライズ大成功だね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan's fan is so happy.\nThe surprise was a huge success!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7433292937,
      "endTime": 83.3030572486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……\nでも、釣りだと私達が手伝えることはなさそうだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nBut it doesn't seem like there's anything we can do to help with fishing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5099959604,
      "endTime": 90.1758688203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.3766626271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない……今日はみんなで釣りをする……！\nその方が楽しいし……ファンの人も喜ぶ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true… We're all fishing together today…!\nIt’ll be more fun that way… and he will be happy…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.3766626271,
      "endTime": 98.04487103550001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.2456648421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "これをきっかけに、みんなのことも好きになる……\nそれが『繋がる』ということ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’ll come to like everyone too with this opportunity…\nThat's what it means to ‘connect’…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2456648421,
      "endTime": 105.0295878005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.2303816072
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "怜ちゃんとさくらちゃんも一緒にしてくれるんですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei-chan and Sakura-chan are joining us too?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.2303816072,
      "endTime": 109.13929671220001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "ファンA",
      "speakerNameEn": "Fan",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あぁ、サニピのファンをやってて良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I'm glad I’m a Sunny Peace fan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1392967122,
      "endTime": 114.32278387449999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.5235776813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに喜ばれたら、やらない訳にはいかないわね\n雫、いろいろと教えてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't say no if he's this happy about it.\nShizuku‚ will you teach me about it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5235776813,
      "endTime": 122.2901084812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.4902443479
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "任せて……！　手取り足取り、しっかり教える……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave it to me…! I’ll teach you everything‚ from start to finish…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4902443479,
      "endTime": 127.0284984182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.2292922249
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "誰が一番多く釣れるか勝負だね！\n負けないぞ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s have a competition to see who can catch the most fish!\nI won't lose~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2292922249,
      "endTime": 133.1849609604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.3959588916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "やけに気合いが入ってるけど\nさくらは釣りしたことあるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're awfully fired up‚\nbut Sakura‚ have you ever fished before?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3959588916,
      "endTime": 138.57208136629998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "うん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7626255582,
      "endTime": 140,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.2292657763
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "二人の釣り竿と仕掛けは用意してある……\n後はエサを付けるだけだから……",
      "translations": {
